r\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"x0i7609\"} -->\n<h2>more about me</h2>\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-divider {\"divider_color\":\"#fcdca9ff\",\"divider_weight\":\"2\",\"divider_widht\":\"7\",\"divider_gap\":\"10\",\"ele_margin\":\"-15px,0px,0px,0px\",\"animation\":\"\",\"animation_speed\":\"slowest\",\"animation_delay\":\"700\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"xk89102\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-text {\"ele_padding\":\"0%,24%,0%,24%\",\"ele_padding_tablet\":[\"0%\",\"0%\",\"0%\",\"0%\"],\"ele_padding_mobile\":\"0px,0px,0px,0px\",\"animation\":\"\",\"animation_speed\":\"slowest\",\"animation_delay\":\"800\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"o3u1437\"} -->\n<p [object NamedNodeMap]>The truth is: I\'m also knowing myself<br>Well, welcome! As you can notice by the name of my personal blog, I\'m Larissa. I\'m creating this place to write about living abroad, my discoveries and something else I think it\'s interesting. <br>​<br>FAQ:<br>Why in english? <br>Because I wanna practice my skills writing in english, built a portfolio and this is the way I found out.</p>\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-heading {\"align\":\"center\",\"ele_padding\":[\"50px\",\"0px\",\"0px\",\"0px\"],\"ele_padding_tablet\":[\"30px\",\"0px\",\"0px\",\"0px\"],\"ele_padding_mobile\":[\"25px\",\"0px\",\"0px\",\"0px\"],\"pagelayer-id\":\"e6k9635\"} -->\n<h4>tips &amp; tricks</h4>\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-heading {\"align\":\"center\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"wuf3325\"} -->\n<h3>how to take a good picture</h3>\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-divider {\"divider_color\":\"#fcdca9ff\",\"divider_weight\":\"2\",\"divider_widht\":\"10\",\"divider_gap\":\"10\",\"ele_margin\":\"-15px,0px,0px,0px\",\"animation\":\"\",\"animation_speed\":\"slowest\",\"animation_delay\":\"800\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"ogn3649\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-image {\"id\":\"7\",\"img_hover_delay\":\"400\",\"animation\":\"\",\"animation_speed\":\"slowest\",\"animati