:pagelayer/pl-col -->\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-row -->\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-col -->\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-row -->\n\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-row {\"col_gap\":\"10\",\"overlay_hover_delay\":\"400\",\"row_shape_top_width\":\"100\",\"row_shape_top_height\":\"100\",\"row_shape_bottom_width\":\"100\",\"row_shape_bottom_height\":\"100\",\"ele_padding\":\"0px,0px,80px,0px\",\"ele_padding_mobile\":\"0px,0px,40px,0px\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"0x85094\"} -->\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-col {\"widget_space\":\"15\",\"overlay_hover_delay\":\"400\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"5c95304\"} -->\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-heading {\"align\":\"center\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"ng7961\"} -->\n<h2>about me</h2>\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-divider {\"divider_color\":\"#fcdca9ff\",\"divider_weight\":\"2\",\"divider_widht\":\"7\",\"divider_gap\":\"10\",\"ele_margin\":\"-15px,0px,0px,0px\",\"animation\":\"\",\"animation_speed\":\"slowest\",\"animation_delay\":\"700\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"f247359\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-text {\"ele_padding\":\"0%,24%,0%,24%\",\"ele_padding_tablet\":[\"0%\",\"0%\",\"0%\",\"0%\"],\"ele_padding_mobile\":\"0px,0px,0px,0px\",\"animation\":\"\",\"animation_speed\":\"slowest\",\"animation_delay\":\"800\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"9b64141\"} -->\n<p [object NamedNodeMap]>The truth is: I\'m also knowing myself<br>Well, welcome! As you can notice by the name of my personal blog, I\'m Larissa. I\'m creating this place to write about living abroad, my discoveries and something else I think it\'s interesting. <br>​<br>FAQ:<br>Why in english? <br>Because I wanna practice my skills writing in english, built a portfolio and this is the way I found out.</p>\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-row {\"col_gap\":\"10\",\"content_pos\":\"center\",\"overlay_hover_delay\":\"400\",\"row_shape_top_width\":\"100\",\"row_shape_top_height\":\"100\",\"row_shape_bottom_width\":\"100\",\"row_shape_bottom_height\":\"100\",\"ele_padding\":\"30px,0px,0px,0px\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"uyk8218\"} -->\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-col {\"widget_space\":\"15\",\"col_width\":\"50\",\"col_width_tablet\":100,\"col_width_mobile\":\"100\",\"overlay_hover_delay\":\"400\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"spp5808\"} -->\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-heading {\"align\":\"left\",\"heading_typo\":[\"\",\"\",\"\",\"\",\"\",\"\",\"Solid\",\"\",\"Capitalize\",\"\",\"\"],\"pagelayer-id\":\"ynd627\"} -->\n<h2>Hi...</h2>\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-text {\"ele_padding\":\"3%,0%,0%,0%\",\"animation\":\"\",\"animation_speed\":\"slowest\",\"animation_delay\":\"700\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"lxx2906\"} -->\n<p [object NamedNodeMap]>De perto e pessoalmente<br>Acredito que sinceridade e autenticidade são essenciais para prosperar no mundo virtual de hoje. Meu blog é um lugar com a missão de celebrar a personalidade, o senso de humor e o coração. A conexão com o mundo foi a minha motivação para começar o(a) Larissa Vasconcelos. Desde que criei este projeto, o blog tem crescido e rapidamente conquistado seguidores leais. Para ver o que tenho feito, navegue pelo meu site, saiba mais sobre o que me motiva e descubra temas interessantes que podem inspirar você também.</p>\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-text {\"ele_padding\":\"3%,0%,0%,0%\",\"animation\":\"\",\"animation_speed\":\"slowest\",\"animation_delay\":\"700\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"iwe6532\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-text {\"ele_padding\":\"0%,0%,0%,0%\",\"animation\":\"\",\"animation_speed\":\"slowest\",\"animation_delay\":\"900\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"eom2183\"} -->\n<span style=\"line-height:2.0\"><p style=\"text-align:left;color:#5d5d5d\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Proin diam justo, scelerisque non felis porta, placerat vestibulum nisi.</p></span>\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-text -->\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-col -->\n\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-col {\"widget_space\":\"15\",\"col_width\":\"50\",\"col_width_tablet\":100,\"overlay_hover_delay\":\"400\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"i8y8123\"} -->\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"100%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\"><!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-image {\"id\":25,\"align\":\"left\",\"img_hover_delay\":\"400\",\"animation\":\"\",\"animation_speed\":\"slowest\",\"animation_delay\":\"700\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"0qj1390\",\"tmpAtts\":{\"id-full-url\":\"http://larissabfv.lovestoblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/IMG_1608_HEIC.webp\",\"id-thumbnail-url\":\"http://larissabfv.lovestoblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/IMG_1608_HEIC-150x150.webp\",\"id-medium-url\":\"http://larissabfv.lovestoblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/IMG_1608_HEIC-225x300.webp\",\"id-medium_large-url\":\"http://larissabfv.lovestoblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/about-1-768x1151.jpg\",\"id-large-url\":\"http://larissabfv.lovestoblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/about-1-683x1024.jpg\",\"id-1536x1536-url\":\"http://larissabfv.lovestoblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/about-1-1025x1536.jpg\",\"id-2048x2048-url\":\"http://larissabfv.lovestoblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/about-1-1367x2048.jpg\",\"id-url\":\"http://larissabfv.lovestoblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/IMG_1608_HEIC.webp\",\"id-alt\":\"\",\"id-title\":\"IMG_1608_HEIC\",\"id-link\":\"http://larissabfv.lovestoblog.com/about-1/\",\"id-no-image-set\":\"\"}} /--></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl-heading {\"align\":\"center\",\"pagelayer-id\":\"pfw1805\"} -->\n<h2>Larisa Vasconcelos</h2>\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-heading -->\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-col -->\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-row -->\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-col -->\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl-row -->', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-07-31 16:49:43', '2024-07-31 16:49:43', '', 14, 'http://larissabfv.lovestoblog.com/?p=26', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(214, 1, '2024-09-23 19:33:05', '2024-09-23 19:33:05', '{\"version\": 3, \"isGlobalStylesUserThemeJSON\": true }', 'Custom Styles', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'wp-global-styles-twentytwentyfour', '', '', '2024-09-23 19:33:05', '2024-09-23 19:33:05', '', 0, 'https://laporai.com/2024/09/23/wp-global-styles-twentytwentyfour/', 0, 'wp_global_styles', '', 0),
(166, 1, '2024-09-23 18:44:32', '2024-09-23 18:44:32', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>...or something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://larissabfv.lovestoblog.com/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Sample Page', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-autosave-v1', '', '', '2024-09-23 18:44:32', '2024-09-23 18:44:32', '', 2, 'https://laporai.com/?p=166', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(36, 1, '2024-08-04 13:57:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Começar um mestrado não fazia parte dos meus planos nem um pouquinho. A decisão veio quando percebi ser a melhor forma de estudar </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Passei no mestrado!', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2024-08-04 13:57:01', '2024-08-04 13:57:01', '', 0, 'http://larissabfv.lovestoblog.com/?p=36', 0, 'post', '', 0),
